data.meta_description:
2,599 likes, 17 comments - nobelprize_org on June 17, 2020: "Happy birthday to Mohamed Elbaradei. “Today, with globalisation bringing us ever closer together, if we choose to ignore the insecurities of some, they will soon become the insecurities of all.” In 2005 the Nobel Peace Prize was awarded to International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) and its Director General, ElBaradei for their efforts to prevent nuclear energy from being used for military purposes and to ensure that nuclear energy for peaceful purposes is used in the safest possible way.

The quote above is from ElBaradei’s Nobel Peace Prize Lecture. Read the full lecture at nobelprize.org

Photo: Dean Calma/IAEA
